    <item>
      <title>The Giver (DVD)</title>
      <link>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2014/11/08/the-giver-dvd/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Nov 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2014/11/08/the-giver-dvd/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure class=&#34;cover-image&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.jverkamp.com/embeds/movies/the-giver.jpg&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Apparently &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff%20Bridges&#34;&gt;Jeff Bridges&lt;/a&gt; has been trying to have The Giver turned into a movie for the better part of two decades. Originally, he wanted to have &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/his%20father&#34;&gt;Lloyd Bridges&lt;/a&gt; in the eponymous role. He even apparently went so far as to have a version filmed somewhere, although so far as I know that version has never been made publically available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I wonder if that one diverged so much from the book?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
